From 0ddb4327d873838ec1c892f24b2617e73e259456 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Mon, 1 Jun 2026 23:46:35 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Redesign site as minimal academic homepage

Rebuild every page in a clean, minimalist academic style inspired by
pascalmichaillat.org / michelefinck.eu:

- Single typeface (Fraunces) everywhere; drop Inter & JetBrains Mono
- Two colours on white: near-black ink + one warm terracotta accent
- Generous whitespace, narrow readable measure, full-width masthead rule
- Prominent portrait + dual identity (legal consultant & scholar) in hero
- Research/publications presented as a clean academic list
- Remove all decorative motion: floating shapes, custom cursor, scroll
  indicators, marquee, reveal/split-text/tilt/magnetic animations
- Simplify header, footer, nav, language switcher, forms and CTAs to
  quiet text links

Also untrack committed .next build artifacts (already in .gitignore).

